Hybrid Races 2026
📆 2 of 12

@rextreme.official 🇰🇷 – 1st Place 🥇 (Prelims; chose not to proceed to finals)
@hyroxjapan Osaka 🇯🇵 Mixed Doubles – 1st Place Overall 🏆
@hyroxjapan Osaka 🇯🇵 Pro Doubles – 1st Place Overall 🏆
@hystorace 🇮🇩 Elite Doubles – 1st Place 🏆

Four races. Four wins.

Started this page even before Captain began competing in Hyrox — so watching the hybrid scene grow and seeing him establish himself among the best hybrid athletes out there has been truly incredible. 🔥

P.S. The backwards run had to stay. Just checking on his partner… but lowkey looked cool too 😌🫶

