Our newest partner @hollylandtech is helping us with audio and video technology to make our production even better for 2025. 

The first device is the Lark M2S wireless microphone. There are lots of wireless microphones on the market but the Lark M2S sounds terrific, has long battery life which is really useful at events, and cuts out unwanted sounds at loud places like race tracks. And it is totally affordable at around $159. 

