A bizarre set of circumstances result in us taking the Sportsman Class win despite finishing *behind* our closest competitors.

Either way, we are happy to have shown our strong race pace on Sunday and are looking forward to seeing what our 2024 car can do once we chase the bugs out of our electronics and aero setups.

Race report and in-car video coming soon!

