In racing dampers are probably the most important component of your car. Almost all of our cara are on @jrzsuspension products. They are a Dutch company that makes some of the best dampers in the world. All are hand made to your specifications and they are amazing. Good dampers make the car easier to drive, inspire more confidence, are safer if you make a mistake and makes set up easier. 

After 11 years of being a customer, GoGoGear is now a dealer of JRZ Suspension products. 

We were lucky enough to visit their fabulous facility in a small town in the Netherlands and meet some of the amazing people that make some of the best cars in the world go faster. Fun fact: they don’t just do racing. They started with racing and have even produced dampers for Formula 1 cars. But these days they also do street cars, track cars, ambulances, military vehicles, armored vehicles and off road machines. But we get the feeling that racing is where their heart is. 

If you need some for your performance car, let us know and we can offer very competitive prices. 

