This whole game is a balancing act. How close can I get to the limit without pushing myself over the edge? That balance point is where I’ll make maximum progress. It’s where intensity and insanity must meet intellect and strategy. Most people think they’re near the edge because they feel a little fatigue. The truth is once you've taken a few hits and realize you're not made of glass, you won’t feel alive until you're pushing it to the absolute limit. #animalmentality 
