Take a day off. One time won't kill you. These poisonous thoughts promote mediocrity and do nothing for your development or mental toughness. It's true, one bad meal won't hurt you and one day missed at the gym won't ruin years of building muscle. But it sure as hell won’t make you progress. Champions don’t think this way. You are not in this game for convenience. This is not a hobby you fit into your life; this is your life. If you want to creep around the gym whenever you feel like it, go somewhere else. Here, on this gym floor, training is all that exists. #AnimalPak 
