Here's another throwback for you:
2008  Bavaria State Junior Class - won the overall at 183 lbs. (83kg) #Shredded  I had no idea how to diet so simply ate nothing but Tilapia and water. NO vegetables, NO other foods or fluids. Period. For three weeks. At that point I had to give in to the exhaustion, dizziness and the fact that I had absolutely nothing left in the tank. I started adding carbs back slowly and managed to bring my weight back up to 190 lbs. Even harder. Two weeks later I also won the German National Junior overall. I'll show those pictures on the next #TBT and continue the story... #AllesAusNichts 
Photo credits to: @niebergallandre
.
