Knee pain is a big issue when it comes to training legs. Wear and tear from chronic use of the knee joints coupled with heavy weight creates difficulties during workouts. Instead of starting your workout with extensions, try warming up with a leg curl. This gets the blood moving from the back of the knee, which will set you up for your training session. Comment below with other questions or topics you’d like me to cover in the next installment of “The 59”. #AnimalPak #The59 #Bodybuilding #BodybuildingTips #LegTraining #LegDay #KneeWarmup 🔺️Für Gelenkschmerzen🔺️ Nirgends günstiger! #AnimalFLEX
